long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
CodeingameSolver is a new Google Chrome extension made to help you with your Codingame tests. Whether you're good at C#, love Python, or prefer JavaScript, this extension is for you. It quickly solves your Codingame challenges without being detected by Codingame's anti-cheating system.

We all know that programming tests might not always show how good a developer really is and can be a bit unfair. That's where CodeingameSolver comes in. It's designed to make things fair by giving you solutions to your Codingame challenges with just one click. It works with many programming languages, from CSS to Docker, Typescript to AngularJs, and Bash to .NET.

Don't settle for just being good â€“ aim to be the best. Whether you're working on problems in C++ or HTML, improving your skills in Angular2+ or ApacheSpark, our extension is here to help you succeed. We have different packages to choose from, like the Discovery Pack, Popular Deal, and Golden Pack. These packages cover Java, Android, Kotlin, and more, giving you everything you need to do well in a Codingame test. If you're looking for a job, our ultimate solution even lets you take Codingame tests for other developers, increasing your chances of getting hired and earning money.

If you need help or have questions, you can contact us at codeingamesolver@gmail.com. We're also here for any programming project you might have.

With CodeingameSolver, your Codingame tests will be a lot easier. Try it out today!
